  "title": "Luxury Goods Appraiser | Up to $3000 |5 Days | Bishan & JEM - ZH",
  "description": "<p>Salary: Basic up to $3000 (Depending on experience)<br />Location: Bishan/JEM<br />Working Hours: 5 Days</p><ul><li>Shift work between 11am – 9pm (Mon–Sun include PH)</li><li>8 hours work + 1 hour break</li></ul><p>Key Duties:</p><ul><li>Appraisal and estimation of brand-name items and precious metals</li><li>Handling first-time customers with care and professionalism</li><li>Shipping preparation and basic store upkeep</li><li>Basic data entry, stock check and daily operations</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Outgoing and comfortable talking to people</li><li>Interest in luxury brands and products</li><li>Detail Oriented</li></ul><p>WhatsApp me at wa.me/6587801169 or press the APPLY NOW BUTTON.</p><p>By submitting your resume and/or personal information, you consent to the collection, use, and disclosure of your personal data by the company (or its designated agent) for the purposes of processing, administration and managing your job application.</p><p>Please be notified that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Sim Shu Hui Reg No.: R25129789<br />Griffin HR Consultancy Pte Ltd | EA License No.: 23C1449</p>",
